모에","body":"이 사아야, 예쁘지~\n찬찬히 보고 싶은 심정도 이해는 돼.\n평소랑은 분위기가 완전 다르잖아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"simizimi01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"나도 사전에 듣지 않았더라면\n단번에 못 알아 봤을 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"사아야가 웨딩드레스를 입은 이유……?\n아하하, 이런저런 일이 있던 것 같던데?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"애초에 시작은 상점가 이웃한테\n모델 제의를 받아서라고 그랬지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"뭐~ 사아야네는 집도 상점가에 있는 가게니까.\n부탁을 받으면 거절하기 힘들지 않겠어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"아니, 사실은 말이야……\n우연히 촬영하는 날에 현장에 가버렸거든……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"진짜 그때는 깜짝 놀랐다니까.\n아코랑 같이 외출하는데\n난데없이 드레스를 입고 있는 사아야를 본 거니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"그렇지~?\n깜짝 놀랐다니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial143-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"아니아니. 순간 누군지 진짜 몰랐는데\n사아야라는 걸 알게 된 순간 머릿속이 혼란스러워졌거든.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChang